<h2>Overview</h2>

<p><a href="https://americanguntrader.com" rel="noopener noreferrer">AmericanGunTrader.com™</a> is a peer-to-peer firearms marketplace built for a community that mainstream platforms have repeatedly failed. While Facebook bans firearms sales outright, and legacy platforms like GunBroker and ArmsList charge listing fees, transaction fees, or both — AmericanGunTrader.com™ operates on a fundamentally different model: core trading is free, forever.</p>

<p>The platform enables users to list firearms for sale or auction, message directly, negotiate, and close deals with zero commission. No listing fees. No transaction fees. The result is a marketplace that aligns with its community rather than extracting from it.</p>

